Let me say this first....Sleeping Dogs is probably one of the GREATEST games I have ever had the pleasure of playing. Oh man this game is so god damn good I have 100% completed it twice and now that I have it on PC I will do it a third time. Sleeping dogs is like if GTA was to meet a cheesy 80's Hong Kong action film but in my opinion feels and plays 10 times better. This game easily gets you into its world with crime, open world exploration and kung fu combat. With its gorgeous environments, tight game play and amazing storytelling it always has me wanting to replay it. Honestly if you have not played this game you are doing yourself an injustice. I have this weird obsession with wanting and not wanting a sequel to this game because it's pretty much perfect as is but also I'd would LOVE another title to this beautiful franchise. Please, PLEASE play this game because it is absolutely an unforgettable experience. #videogames #gaming #sleepingdogs #mustplay #openworld #xbox #ps4 #pc #perfect #oneofmyfavoritegames #amazing #mustplay #underrated #completed #oneofmyfavs @xbox @playstation @steam @squareenix

caption.text:
What's your favorite part of game collecting?
.
.
Mine is discovering new games I've never heard of to play. Rise of Kasai is one of those games. I recently acquired this game at the Long Island Retro Game Expo. I'd previously played the games prequel, The Mark of Kri, and I wanted to get a chance to play the sequel. The games feature some unique combat mechanics which I look forward to exploring. .
.
Make sure you check out the latest episode of the @regionfreegamerspodcast and we'll be dropping a bonus episode this Thursday for y'all so be ready for it! You can find the show on Itunes, Spotify, Youtube and all your favorite podcast providers.
.

To prepare for the new Modern Warfare i started off with the one that kicked the series into new heights. Bare in mind I played the remaster version. This is a solid game even in today standards. A short but impactful campaign that has good Characters, great set pieces and tight gameplay. In terms of arcade action you can't get any better then this. The multiplayer is as good as it's always been with the creating a class and adding attachments and skins. There are problems of course. First off the loot box system is horrible. I hate it and screw Activision for putting it in here and screw them harder for making dlc maps for a remaster...dlc. Activision really don't care. And for me I played it through veteran and I get it. It's hardest difficulty but you do sometimes feel really unfair. I lost count how many times I'd fight the same enemy after a checkpoint restart and it always be random if I'd have time to shoot him or he'd snap to me and kill me quicker then I can aim down sight's. Our felt very unfair. Apart from that the game is great and set in stone a series that would make way for a generation of gamers. But what did you guys and gals think? Let me know and I'll see you guys... In the next post.  #game #Games #gaming #videogame #videogames #callofduty #callofduty4modernwarfare #callofduty4remastered

This game took me by surprise the first time I played it. One of the best stories in any game I’ve ever played. Bought the PS3 and PS4 version, as well as the art book and comic book. Loved this game. It came out right before my daughter was born, and I think it helped me transition into parenthood. I really don’t know if the sequel will live up to the hype, but I’ll keep my fingers crossed. #TheLastOfUs

caption.text:
Borderlands 3 é o quarto jogo de uma franquia que completa 10 anos de existência e que precisava urgentemente se renovar! Toda a saga é baseada em ser um shooter looter, o tipo de jogo que é baseado em atirar, lotear e melhorar seu personagem constantemente, sendo isso então o que o jogo se propõe a fazer e faz de uma forma excelente. 
Definitivamente é um jogo que não se deve levar a sério pois nem mesmo ele se leva, humor esse game tem de sobra alem de muitas horas de jogo, elementos de RPG, gameplay frenético, diversidade e coop com tela dividida, algo muito raro nos dias dê hoje. Se você gosta de um bom game de tiro e se identifica com tudo isso, Borderlands 3 é para você!

PONTOS POSITIVOS
- Gameplay Frenético - 4 classes com inúmeras builds possíveis
- Variedade inacabável de armas(literalmente)
- Conteúdo pós game extenso
- Bem humorado
- Locais variados
- Grande quantidade de inimigos

PONTOS NEGATIVOS
- O game só implementa certa dificuldade depois do new game +
- Problemas de performance - Bugs que podem ser chatos como desligamento da IA
- Você pode não se identificar com o humor que o jogo trás e acabar achando besta

Nota: 8,0 - Se você já gostava da saga, certamente vai gostar do novo, porem se nunca jogou borderlands sugiro que jogue os anteriores que sempre estão em promoção, a chance de você gostar é grande principalmente se jogar com um amigo !

caption.text:
🚀 Rebel Galaxy Outlaw 🚀
.
Ahondando en la acción en tercera persona, nos presentará un mundo espacial con una serie de misiones que ofrecerán más de 20 horas de jugabilidad a los usuarios. Su historia se ambienta 34 años de los hechos del anterior juego y nos lleva a un sistema solar más próximo a la Tierra. Nos pone en el papel de Juno Markev, un fuera de la ley que decidió alejarse de ese mundo y llevar una vida tranquila. Sin embargo, ahora una serie de hechos le obligan a abandonar su retiro voluntario y pagar una deuda a viejos conocidos. •
